reasons.another: User ne pehle is server se disconnect kiye bina seedha kisi aur server se connect kar liya.
reasons.banned: Is user ko diye gaye karan ke saath ek staff member ne ban kiya.
reasons.config: Jab servers connect ho rahe the to configuration load nahi ho paayi jiski wajah se user ko reject kar diya gaya.
reasons.crash: User ke game ne diye gaye error message ke saath crash kiya.
reasons.disconnected: User ne F8 console ya us jaise kisi me 'disconnect' likh kar server se disconnect kiya.
reasons.doors: Server ne client ke saath darwazon ko synchronize karne ki koshish ki par fail ho gaya, isliye user ko kick kar diya gaya kyunki is error se wapas nahin aaya ja sakta.
reasons.editor: Player ne apna Rockstar Editor khola jo turant aapke current server ko chhod deta hai.
reasons.exited: User ne F8 console me 'quit' type kar ke ya ALT+F4 dabakar ya is jaise kisi tareeke se game se bahar nikal diya.
reasons.global: System ne yeh paaya ki user shayad kuch malicious kar raha tha aur global OP-FW ban de diya.
reasons.job: User ki job priority ki avadhi khatam ho gayi. Iska matlab hai ki user job priority ke liye queue mein bahut der tak tha, isliye system ne use queue se nikaal diya.
reasons.kicked: User ko diye gaye karan ke saath staff sadasya dwara nikaala gaya.
reasons.overflow: FiveM dwara aapke server ko events se cheaters ke spam se bachav ke liye suraksha upaay.
reasons.reloading_game: User ne F8 console ya uske milte-julte command se 'localGame' command ka upyog karke single-player game load ki.
reasons.restart: Server restart ho raha tha isliye user ko server dwara nikaal diya gaya.
reasons.timeout: Server se user ki connection timeout ho gayi. Aksar aisa tab hota hai jab internet connectivity drop out ho jaati hai.
reasons.unknown: Vistaar se varnan uplabdh nahi hai. Jyada madad ke liye aap kisi developer se pooch sakte hain.

detail.title: Vistaar se disconnect ka karan

staff_statistics.description: Karmchariyon ke baare mein kuch samanya statistics.
staff_statistics.description_chinese: Aapke samajik samarasya aur pragati mein kiye gaye yogdan ka ek vistaarit record, sabke fayde ke liye Party dwara niyantrit. Yaad rakhiye, har karm aapke samuhik bhavishya ke pratigya ko darshata hai.
staff_statistics.footer: Aapke kary OP-FW ki safalta aur vriddhi mein yogdan dete hain. OP-Framework ki bharosemand pranaliyon ke madhyam se aapke prayas ko pehchana jaata hai aur hamari samuhik pragati ka hissa banaaya jaata hai. Teamwork uplabdhi ko badhaata hai, aur lagan shreshhta banata hai. OP-FW ki jai!
staff_statistics.footer_chinese: Jo bhi kaam aap karte hain, vo Party ke prati aapki vafadari aur pratibaddhata ka saboot hai. System ki nigahen rehne ke dauran aapke yogdan darj kiye jaate hain aur hamari samuhik pragati ka hissa banaye jaate hain. Aagya ka palan samriddhi laata hai, aur chetna se samriddhi ki guarantee milti hai. CCP ki jai!
staff_statistics.level_0_description: Jab aap staff path par kadam rakh chuke hain, to aapki kshamata ab bhi sookhi padhi hui aur akar-ladh nahi hai. Aap guruon ki fuzool baaton se gyaan prapt karte hain aur rajya ki urjaen aapke charo taraf ghummti hui jigyasa se bharti hain. Mahanta ke beej aapki pakad mein hain, bas vah pal aane ki pratiksha jo aap aage badhkar unhe paayein.
staff_statistics.level_10_description: Kahaaniyaan aapki atirikt unnatata ki baat karti hain, ek aisi kiran jo keval maujoodgi se sabse toofani aandhiyon ko bhi shant kar deti hai. Aapki staff ki urja har kona mein gunjti hai, jod banake un logon ke beech jo aapki nigarani mein hain. Is manav bal ki choti par, aap apne drid nirdeshon se duniya ki kismet banaate hain.
staff_statistics.level_1_description: Akhirkaar, staff ki jaadu ki pehli chamak tumhaare haath mein chamak rahi hai, jo tumhaare jawaabon ko chhoti server samasyaon par raah dikhata hai. Tum taiyaar ho ki kabhi-kabhi hue jhagra ko shaant karo ya pal ki ashanti ko daba do, apni keemat sabit karne ki utsaah ke saath. Jaadu ka daur har madad ki pukaar ke saath aur mazboot hota jaata hai, uchch maharat ki pratigya ko jagata hai.
staff_statistics.level_2_description: Server ko chalane wale naazuk pravah ko gale lagate hue, tum reports aur disciplinary kadamon ko ubharti hui kala ke saath chaturai se sambhaal lete ho. Aawaz ki garaj ki jagah kam hoti hai jab tumhara sangathit vyavhaar aur tezi se kiye gaye nirnay shanti ko banaye rakhte hain. Har kriya tumhe is realm ki tasveer me aur gehraai se jodti hai, iski safaarti ki dridhta ko mazboot karti hai.
staff_statistics.level_3_description: Aapki adhyatmik wardon aur banishing mantro ki pakad server ko ek sthir shaanti mein jodti hai. Shaitaani log aapki chaukasi se haar jaate hain, aur aapka chamakta hua staff prashasan ki roshni ki nishaani ki tarah khada hai. Chahe chhuppe hue saaye kitni bhi gehri kyun na ho, aapki avibhajit samarpan pareshani ko vijay me badal deti hai.
staff_statistics.level_4_description: Sabse andhere konon se, tum dekh rahe ho, rajya ko khatre mein daalne wali sabse naazuk muskurahat ki halki si chingari par bhi nazar rakhe hue. Tez zimmedariyan aur sahi hastakshep tumhari bhumika ko ek majboot guardian ki roop mein darshata hai, is kshetra mein koi bhi dushman der tak tikta nahi. Vyavastha aur chaos ke beech ki parda tumhari sakriya najar ke neeche surakshit tarah se jura rehta hai.
staff_statistics.level_5_description: Swargiya shaktiyaan aapke faislon ko margdarjit karti hain, aapko brahmand ki kripa ke saath samvad sthapit karne ki shakti deti hain jisse samanvay bana raha. Sansar aapse santulit nirnayon ki apeksha karta hai, aapki kshamata par bharosa karta hai ki aap sangharsh ko daba sakte hain aur zaruratmandon ko uthaa sakte hain. Har din ke saath, astral urjaon ki aapki maharat badh rahi hai, jo staff aur players dono ke liye raah roshni ki tarah roshan karti hai.
staff_statistics.level_6_description: Aapki staff prabal shakti ke saath gunjti hai, shighr prasaar ke saath sthir roopak ko door karti hai. Aapke naam ki keval yaad se hi asahaya logon me darr ki lehar daur jaati hai, kyunki ve jaante hain ki aapka ghrina kisi ko nahi chhodega jo rajya ko hilaye. Phir bhi itni taakat ke saath aap nyaay ko dhyan me rakhte hain, sunishchit karte hain ki nyaay nyaayik roop se aur nishpakshata se diya jaye.
staff_statistics.level_7_description: Aakaashiya adhikaar ki chamak se aap rajya ke rakshakon ki sena ko ki niti me laate hain aur ashaanti ko paanv jamaane se pehle hi shant kar dete hain. Aapke legendary hastakshepon ki khabrein door tak jaati hain, sab ke liye margdarshak sita ki sthiti majboot karti hain. Aapke yogya haath mein, server ka bhavishya roshan bana rehta hai, andhkaar se bahar.
staff_statistics.level_8_description: Aap roshni aur andhkaar ki seema par chalte hain, aapsi vyakhya ke roop me chaos ki chhupe hue dhaagon ko pehle hi padh lete hain. Tezi se thande padna aur mahir kadam aapki shanti banaye rakhne ki bhakti sabit karte hain, bache hue khatron ko koi sthaan nahi dete. Aapki sookshmta aur shakti ki mil-jul se yah sunishchit hota hai ki jo koi bhi aapke daayere me rahta hai, wah samvaad me harmonium me rahta hai.
staff_statistics.level_9_description: Anek sangharshon ke beech, aap ki maharat manav seemaon se aage nikal gayi hai, rannitigya chalaakī ko ek sthir naitik disha ke saath milakar. Trolls aur troublemakers aapke aage gaayab ho jaate hain, har ban ya mute ek santulit badlaav ki kala ke roop me. Is pavitra sthiti mein, aap ki samarpan is vishwa ki atoot drirhta ki misal hai.
